Teams with a valid Season Pass licenses can use Phoenix Pro on a robot configured with any of the off-season demo team numbers.
https://v6.docs.ctr-electronics.com/en/latest/docs/licensing/team-licensing.html#when-is-a-season-pass-applicable

CTRE does not offer a free license.
You are able to use Phoenix 6 simulation to demo pro features.
https://v6.docs.ctr-electronics.com/en/latest/docs/licensing/what-is-licensing.html
